{"ja318:0.1":"Jataka ","ja318:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja318:0.3":"Pucimandavagga ","ja318:0.4":"8. Kanaverajataka ","ja318:1.1":"“Yam tam vasantasamaye, ","ja318:1.2":"kanaveresu bhanusu; ","ja318:1.3":"Samam bahaya pilesi, ","ja318:1.4":"sa tam arogyamabravi”. ","ja318:2.1":"“Ambho na kira saddheyyam, ","ja318:2.2":"yam vato pabbatam vahe; ","ja318:2.3":"Pabbatance vahe vato, ","ja318:2.4":"sabbampi pathavim vahe; ","ja318:2.5":"Yattha sama kalakata, ","ja318:2.6":"sa mam arogyamabravi”. ","ja318:3.1":"“Na ceva sa kalakata, ","ja318:3.2":"na ca sa annamicchati; ","ja318:3.3":"Ekabhattikini sama, ","ja318:3.4":"tameva abhikankhati”. ","ja318:4.1":"“Asanthutam mam cirasanthutena, ","ja318:4.2":"Nimini sama adhuvam dhuvena; ","ja318:4.3":"Mayapi sama nimineyya annam, ","ja318:4.4":"Ito aham durataram gamissan”ti. ","ja318:5.1":"Kanaverajatakam atthamam. "}